               <p>SECOND COUNT for lik offence in the dwelling house of 
               <persName id="t18090215-72-person637">
                  John 
                  Bellamy Plowman
               <interp inst="t18090215-72-person637" type="surname" value="Bellamy Plowman"></interp>
